data.Sentence_cn: 已经有人打开窗户了吗？
data.Sentence: Has anyone opened the window yet?

data.Sentence_cn: 是的，它已经被打开了。
data.Sentence: Yes, it has already been opened.

data.Sentence_cn: 有人修改过这些练习册吗?
data.Sentence: Has anyone corrected these exercise books yet?

data.Sentence_cn: 是的，它们已经被改过了。
data.Sentence: Yes, they have already been corrected.

data.Sentence_cn: 会有人扫地吗？
data.Sentence: Will anyone sweep the floor?

data.Sentence_cn: 是的，很快就有人扫。
data.Sentence: Yes, it'll be swept soon.

data.Sentence_cn: 会有人告诉他们吗？
data.Sentence: Will anyone tell them about it?

data.Sentence_cn: 是的，他们很快就会被告知。
data.Sentence: Yes, they'll be told about it soon.

data.Sentence_cn: 已经有人邀请他们了吗？
data.Sentence: Has anyone invited them yet?

data.Sentence_cn: 是的，他们已经被邀请了。
data.Sentence: Yes, they have already been invited.

data.Sentence_cn: 会有人接待他吗？
data.Sentence: Will anyone serve him?

data.Sentence_cn: 是的，不久就有人接待他。
data.Sentence: Yes, he'll be served soon.

data.Sentence_cn: 这辆车已经有人修了吗？
data.Sentence: Has anyone repaired this car yet?

data.Sentence_cn: 是的，它已经被修了。
data.Sentence: Yes, it has already been repaired.

data.Sentence_cn: 会有人找到他们吗？
data.Sentence: Will anyone find them?

data.Sentence_cn: 是的，他们会很快被找到的。
data.Sentence: Yes, they'll be found soon.

data.Sentence_cn: 有人磨这把刀了吗？
data.Sentence: Has anyone sharpened this knife yet?

data.Sentence_cn: 是的，它已经被磨了。
data.Sentence: Yes, it has already been sharpened.

data.Sentence_cn: 会有人磨这些刀吗？
data.Sentence: Will anyone sharpen these knives?

data.Sentence_cn: 是的，它们很快就会被磨的。
data.Sentence: Yes, they'll be sharpened soon.

title.title_cn: 还没有人来招待他。很快会有人来招待他的。
title.title: He has not been served yet. He will be served soon.
